        <div class="foreground how-to-media-large"><div class="how-to-heading">
            
          <h2 id="how-to-edit-pdf-files-online" class="heading-xl">How to edit PDF files online</h2><p>Edit your PDF with Adobe Acrobat, the company that invented the PDF. Just upload your PDF, sign in with your free Adobe account, and start editing in seconds. Annotate, highlight, fill out forms, and sign documents directly in your browser — no installation required. Easily add comments or markups to a PDF online by following these steps.</p></div><div class="how-to-media how-to-media-large"><span class="modal-img-link"><picture>
